quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  35,41,Ngempela uMvelinqangi uyawabamba amazulu nomhlaba ukuthi angasuki endaweni yawo futhi uma esuka endaweni yawo akekho ngisho noyedwa ongawabamba womabili emva kwakhe ngempela yena ngasosonke isikhathi uyabekezela uyathethelela
  35,42,Futhi bafunga ngoMvelinqangi izifungo zabo ezinqala ukuthi uma kungase kufike umxwayisi kubona bangaba ngabaholwe kakhulu ngaphezu kwanoma yiziphi izizwe kepha kwathi lapho sekufika umxwayisi kubona abazange banezelelwe yilutho ngaphandle kokukugwema lokho
  35,43,Beqhosha emhlabeni futhi benza icebo elibi futhi icebo elibi alimsingathi omunye umuntu ngaphandle kwabantu balo ngakho-ke ngakube kukhona yini abakulindele ngaphandle kwendlela yasemandulo na? Kepha awusoze uyifumane inguquko endleleni kaMvelinqangi futhi awusoze ukufumane ukuchezuka endleleni kaMvelinqangi
  35,44,Abazange yini bahambe ezweni babone ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho salabo ababengaphambilini kwabo futhi babeqatha ngamandla kunabo futhi uMvelinqangi akukho lutho elimphunyukayo emazulwini nasemhlabeni futhi yena ngasosonke isikhathi uyazi unamandla okwenza
  35,45,Futhi ukube uMvelinqangi wayengase abajezise abantu ngenxa yalokho abakusebenzele wayengeke azishiye izidalwa ezinyakazayo (izilwane) phezu kwawo (umhlaba) kepha ubayekela isikhathi esinqunyiwe ngakho-ke uma kufika isikhathi sabo ngempela uMvelinqangi ngasosonke isikhathi ungumboni wezinceku zakhe
  36,1,Ya’ seen
  36,2,NgeQur’an enobuhlakani
  36,3,Ngempela wena ungomunye wezithunywa
  36,4,Endleleni eqondile
  36,5,Isambulo sophakeme ngamandla onesihawu
  36,6,Ukuze wexwayise abantu ababengaxwayiswanga oyise ngakho- ke bona abanakile
  36,7,Ngempela izwi laqiniseka kwabaningi babo kepha bona bakholwa
  36,8,Ngempela thina sibeke amaketango ezintanyeni zabo afinyelela ezilevini ukuze amakhanda abo abheke phezulu
  36,9,Futhi sibeke okuvimbelayo ngaphambi kwabo nokumvimbelayo ngemva kwabo sabe sesiyabamboza ukuze bangaboni
  36,10,"Futhi\tkuyefana\tkubona\tnoma\tuyabaxwayisa\tnoma awubaxwayisi angeke bakholwe"
  36,11,"Kuphela ungakwazi ukuxwayisa lowo olandela isikhumbuzo futhi owesaba onomusa ongabonwayo, ngakho-ke mnike izindaba ezimnandi ngentethelelo nangomvuzo osezingeni eliphezulu"
  36,12,"Ngempela\tthina\tsiyabaphilisa\tabafile\rfuthi\rsikubhala phansi lokho abakubeke ngaphambili\rkanye\r(nalokho) okusezinyathelweni\tzabo\tfuthi\tzonke\rizinto\rsizibhalile emholini ocacile"
  36,13,Futhi benzele isibonelo sabantu bedolobha ngenkathi kufika kulona izithunywa
  36,14,Ngenkathi sithumela kubona (izithunywa) ezimbili base beyaziphika zombili sabe sesiyabaqinisa ngowesithathu basebethi “ngempela thina sithunyiwe kunina
  36,15,Bathi (abantu bedolobha) “nina aniyilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngabantu abafana nathi futhi onomusa akazange ambule lutho kuphela nina niqamba amanga”
  36,16,Zathi (izithunywa) “Inkosi yethu iyazi ukuthi thina siyizithunywa kunina”
  36,17,Futhi alikho icala kuthina ngaphandle kokudlulisela umyalezo ocacile
  36,18,"Bathi, “ngempela thina sibona ukubikezela okubi kunina uma ningaphezi ngempela sizonikhanda ngamatshe futhi nizothintwa yisijeziso esibuhlungu esivela kuthina”"
  36,19,"Zathi (izithunywa), “ukubikezela kwenu kukanye nani ngoba nikhunjuzisiwe kepha nina ningabantu abephula umthetho”"
  36,20,Futhi kwafika indoda ivela engxenyeni ebuqamama yedolobha igijima yathi “Oh Bantu bami! landelani izithunywa”
  36,21,Landelani labo abangawuceli umvuzo kunina futhi bona bangabaholelwe endleleni elungileyo
  36,22,Futhi kungani ukuthi ngingamkhonzi lowo owangidalayo futhi niyobubuyiselwa kuyena
  36,23,"Ngakube ngingazithathela omunye uNkulunkulu wamanga esikhundleni sakhe kulapho onomusa ehlose inhlupheko kumina na?, angeke kungisize ngalutho ukungincengela kwabo futhi angeke bangisindise"
  36,24,Ngempela mina ngiyobe ngisekudukeni okucacile
  36,25,Ngempela mina ngikholiwe eNkosini yenu ngakho-ke ngilaleleni
  36,26,"Kwathiwa, “ngena esivandeni (ezulwini)” wathi, “ngifisa sengathi abantu bami bangazi”"
  36,27,Ngokuthi iNkosi yami ingithethelele futhi yangibeka kanye nabahloniphekileyo